name: Trance Sector: Competition Edition
overview: Enjoy 32 new levels, harder gameplay, less lives. Compete! Challenge your friends. The game takes place on an unnamed planet in a deadly nuclear reactor created by alien race known as the 'Cygma Elite'. You must guide your craft around 32 levels collecting the radioactive nuclear pods while avoiding obstacles and enemy seekers. Can you reach the end of the TRANCE SECTOR to eliminate this deadly alien threat?
